#

Overnight Oats with Fruit

10 min
$2.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Dairy (if using milk or yogurt)Nuts (if added)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free OptionHigh Fiber

Cuisine:

AmericanHealthy

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastEasyHealthyMake-Ahead

Description

A creamy, nutritious breakfast that you can prepare in minutes the night before, topped with your favorite fruits!

Ingredients

  • rolled oats: 1/2 cup
  • milk (or dairy-free alternative): 1 cup
  • yogurt (optional): 1/4 cup
  • honey or maple syrup: 1 tbsp
  • chia seeds: 1 tbsp
  • fresh fruits (e.g., berries, banana): 1/2 cup
  • nuts or seeds (optional): 2 tbsp
